pageContext.claim: “I didn't use presidential privilege because I didn't speak to Russia. Russia has -- when I was winning is Wisconsin, when I was winning in Michigan and Pennsylvania and Ohio and Florida and all of these states, North Carolina, the last person or group I ever thought of calling would be Russia.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump literally said, “Russia, if you're listening, I hope you're able to find the 30,000 emails that are missing,” during a July 2016 news conference.
